Added Vereador-specific transformers: `_transform_biografia` HTML-unescapes the biography text, `_transform_image` proxies the photo through `@@images` with Plone's configured scales, `_transform_description` promotes the original description to `fullname` and replaces `description` with the current party token, and `_transform_collections` rewrites nested `@id` URLs for `mandatos`, `mesas`, and `comissoes`. @ericof
